    "team_level": {
      "headline": "A 3v2 midfield overload strangled France's supply line",
      "summary": "Spain's midfield three of Rodri, Fabián Ruiz and Dani Olmo consistently outnumbered France's double pivot of Adrien Rabiot and Aurélien Tchouaméni. France intended to press high to disrupt Spain's rhythm, but the press lacked coordination, so Rodri and Ruiz were repeatedly afforded time and space to dictate tempo.",
      "quote": {
        "speaker": "Kylian Mbappé",
        "point": "described facing repeated 3-vs-2 situations in midfield as the central tactical problem, and said France's press lacked communication"
